      • getValue

        public final Object getValue()
        Returns the value of a Name reference in a MVEL program whose name is given by the return value of this NameResolver's getName() method.

        If a suitable value cannot be determined, then the empty string ("") is returned.

        This method never returns null.

        Specified by:
